---

<section id="aqui-va-dirigit" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
  <div class="container-section">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <span class="badge mb-6">ELS NOSTRES CLIENTS</span>
      <h2 class="section-title mb-6">
        Som el teu partner <span class="text-gradient">ideal</span> si ets...
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Tant si ets una empresa consolidada com una startup ambiciosa, tenim la solució perfecta per a les teves necessitats de comerç electrònic a Catalunya.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Card 1: B2B -->
      <div class="card-base group text-center hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-ecomm-blue hover:to-ecomm-turquoise transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-ecomm-turquoise to-ecomm-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-all duration-500">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h6m-6 4h6m-6 4h6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-ecomm-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Empreses B2B</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-white/90 transition-colors">
          Amb processos de compra complexos que necessiten un portal de clients a mida, preus per volum i integració amb ERP.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: B2C -->
      <div class="card-base group text-center hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-ecomm-blue hover:to-ecomm-turquoise transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-ecomm-turquoise to-ecomm-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-all duration-500">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-ecomm-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Marques B2C</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-white/90 transition-colors">
          Que busquen un disseny excepcional, una experiència d'usuari memorable i una alta taxa de conversió per vendre directament al consumidor.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Migració -->
      <div class="card-base group text-center hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-ecomm-blue hover:to-ecomm-turquoise transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-ecomm-turquoise to-ecomm-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-all duration-500">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-ecomm-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Negocis en creixement</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-white/90 transition-colors">
          Que necessiten migrar des de plataformes obsoletes o limitades cap a solucions més robustes, escalables i personalitzades.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Startups -->
      <div class="card-base group text-center hover:bg-gradient-to-br hover:from-ecomm-blue hover:to-ecomm-turquoise transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-ecomm-turquoise to-ecomm-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-all duration-500">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-ecomm-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Startups Innovadores</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-white/90 transition-colors">
          Amb models de negoci eCommerce disruptius que requereixen un desenvolupament a mida i una base tecnològica sòlida per créixer ràpidament.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
